means: 同 teddy bear(常用于儿语)

tr: plaything consisting of a child's toy bear (usually plush and stuffed with soft materials)

value.def: A teddy is the same as a teddy bear. Children often call their teddies 'Teddy' when they are talking to them or about them.
value.tran: 同 teddy bear（常用于儿语）

trans: 罗斯福；西奥多·罗斯福；泰迪罗斯福；泰迪熊；罗斯福总统
